QuestData.Title: A Green Ogron?
QuestData.Description: Them botani got themselves a green ogron. A green ogron!$b$bI mean I may not know much about plant people but that canno' be a good thing.$b$bThink ya can take it in a fight?
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: One of the more dangerous infested creatures in the botani arsenal.
QuestData.CompletionText: Ogron are ornery enough. I dunna think we need angrier plant ones on top of that.
QuestData.RewardText: Is it still twitchin'? I think I saw it still twitchin'.
